title: Gossip | Rose Byrne and Bobby Cannavale are expecting their first child. Check out her pregnancy style
text:
Congrats to the couple! 36-year-old Byrne and 45-year-old Boardwalk Empire actor Bobby began dating in 2012, and have starred alongside each other in such films as Adult Beginners and Annie.
BABY BUMP! Rose Byrne Is Pregnant with her first child in partnership with Bobby Cannavale https://t.co/BIrXtwWDuA pic.twitter.com/ZSZCwL3TFD
— PENTHAUZE MUSICS (Í â‰– (@PenthauzeMusics) October 23, 2015
Snap at airport shows Rose Byrne is pregnant. https://t.co/yEu6cQWyjP pic.twitter.com/cxzx94A5kQ
— The Daily Telegraph (@dailytelegraph) October 23, 2015 If you're thinking - "I'd know idea they were even dating, never mind expecting a child" - that's OK. They've both been rather quiet regarding their union. In fact, one of the only references to it was when Cannavale thanked her during his 2013 Emmys speech, saying "And I want to thank the love of my life, Rose."
Meanwhile, one of the only references the Aussie actress has made to her relationship was when she announced she wasn't a romantic person during an interview with Elle Canada: "To be honest, I'm not naturally that much of a romantic person - Australians don't like making a fuss. I have trouble with things that feel very manufactured, like Valentine's Day. I'm trying to get better at romance."
Via Us Weekly
